ZH: 我们必须关注社会底层的生活状况。
EN: We must pay attention to the living conditions of the lower social strata.

ZH: 底层人民往往面临更多的困难。
EN: People at the bottom of society often face more difficulties.

ZH: 他们是城市底层的一部分。
EN: They are part of the urban underclass.

ZH: 底层社会需要更多帮助。
EN: The underclass society needs more assistance.

ZH: 很多人生活在社会的底层。
EN: Many people live at the bottom of society.

ZH: 在城市底层，贫困是一个普遍问题。
EN: Poverty is a common issue in the city's underclass.

ZH: 底层劳工往往得不到公平的待遇。
EN: Bottom-level workers often do not receive fair treatment.

ZH: 底层家庭有时无法满足基本需求。
EN: Lower-class families sometimes cannot meet basic needs.

ZH: 底层教育资源短缺。
EN: Educational resources are limited for the lower class.

ZH: 底层人口增加了贫困率。
EN: The increase in the lower-class population has raised the poverty rate.

ZH: 底层居民面临更高的健康风险。
EN: Lower-class residents face higher health risks.

ZH: 底层社会是改变的重中之重。
EN: It is crucial to address the underclass society.

ZH: 底层工作者需要更好的薪酬和福利。
EN: Bottom-tier workers need better wages and benefits.

ZH: 在底层，社会不公是普遍的现象。
EN: In the underclass, social injustice is a common phenomenon.

ZH: 底层问题需要社会的关注。
EN: The issues of the underclass need societal attention.

ZH: 底层人口往往沦为社会弱势群体。
EN: The lower-class population often becomes a marginalized group in society.

ZH: 底层阶层中存在不平等现象。
EN: There are inequalities within the lower strata.

ZH: 底层社会中的儿童更容易受到伤害。
EN: Children in the underclass society are more susceptible to harm.

ZH: 底层居民对社会发展具有重要意义。
EN: Lower-class residents are of great significance to social development.

ZH: 底层群体的声音需要被听到。
EN: The voices of the underclass need to be heard.
